page.title: 18THOSE WHO TOOK PART
page.content: Tanya Case Sadie Young Caroline Smith Lisa Honeyman Paula Brabbing Yvonne Wright Karen Holley Claire Cerson Kim Mead Dawn Shepherd Ryan Ladbrook Luke Young Nicholas Howells Lee Paterson Jo_ann Kendell Samantha Martin Spencer Cappi Alec Schubert Sharon Peters Tracey Brenchley Sonia Templeton Daniel Stobbs Neil Ashdown Mr. Ollett Mr. Griffiths Miss Hutchison. Visits were made to three farms,the sand pit,the church,the heronry and Barling Creek. Visitors invited to the school were Miss Bentall, P.C. Pickering and Mrs. Snow. A traffic and house to house survey were carried out. Information was given by the Evening Echo and the Yacht Club.
